data.description: Relax on this 19,527sqft lot rancher with RV parking & hookups, att double garage, and det single garage. Bright living spaces with skylights in both kitchen and mn flr family rm. With a large fenced backyard and shaded patio it will be the perfect location for a hot tub and space for your pet to roam. Complete with 2 fireplaces, walk-in closet, main flr laundry, and 11 rooms in total; there is plenty room for the whole family to enjoy. Recent updates include new Central a/c unit and $2500 credit toward buyers for updated carpet. Situated in a family-friendly cul-de-sac less than a mile from the nearest shopping, gas, food, bank, and gym. This home is sure to go fast! Book a showing today!
